---
title: Chorizo and Pepper Tortas with Lime Crema Slaw
description: Tortas are Mexican-style sandwiches made with ground meat and a whole lot of delicious fillings! In this version, toasted sub rolls are stuffed with chorizo in a zippy chipotle sauce and roasted peppers and onions. A DIY lime slaw can be piled on the torta or served on the side!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/tortas-au-chorizo-et-aux-poivrons-979ab11c.jpg
